name: Frills And Thrills
summary: The Natural Card Holder is the perfect wallet to save space inside your jacket. Ideal for travel and front-pocket carry, this little wallet can pack a lot. Easily split it into your t-shirt pocket or jeans pocket and barely notice it's there.
description: Full-grain Horween leather means this wallet will develop character and patina. We hand-sew this wallet with thick Tiger Thread for decades of use. We also burnish and polish the wallet edges which adds refinement to the finished piece. Our minimalist design allows you to carry all your essential cards and folded cash without the extra bulk. We take a lot of pride in our work and back each wallet with a lifetime guarantee.

description: Full-grain Horween leather means this wallet will develop character and patina. We hand-sew this wallet with thick Tiger Thread for decades of use. We also burnish and polish the wallet edges which adds refinement to the finished piece. Our minimalist design allows you to carry all your essential cards and folded cash without the extra bulk. We take a lot of pride in our work and back each wallet with a lifetime guarantee.

description: Full-grain Horween leather means this wallet will develop character and patina. We hand-sew this wallet with thick Tiger Thread for decades of use. We also burnish and polish the wallet edges which adds refinement to the finished piece. Our minimalist design allows you to carry all your essential cards and folded cash without the extra bulk. We take a lot of pride in our work and back each wallet with a lifetime guarantee.

description: Full-grain Horween leather means this wallet will develop character and patina. We hand-sew this wallet with thick Tiger Thread for decades of use. We also burnish and polish the wallet edges which adds refinement to the finished piece. Our minimalist design allows you to carry all your essential cards and folded cash without the extra bulk. We take a lot of pride in our work and back each wallet with a lifetime guarantee.
